It's only superficial light

973
00:59:35,241 --> 00:59:37,607
We'll take it just the way it is.

974
00:59:37,676 --> 00:59:40,941
- Alan, I don't need a place this fancy.
- Really?

975
00:59:41,013 --> 00:59:43,641
Maybe we should get Avedon
to do a photo shoot of you...

976
00:59:43,716 --> 00:59:47,015
at the Hotel Roosevelt, at home.

977
00:59:47,086 --> 00:59:50,954
I want to claim as mine

978
00:59:51,023 --> 00:59:57,622
Fancy clothes, a magic coach
and happy ever after

979
00:59:57,696 --> 00:59:59,891
- Like something from a storybook
- Get over there.

980
00:59:59,965 --> 01:00:02,798
- A Cinderella chapter
- She's coming over.

981
01:00:02,868 --> 01:00:05,530
But when the clock strikes midnight

982
01:00:05,604 --> 01:00:08,767
And I lie awake in bed

983
01:00:08,841 --> 01:00:11,708
These lines the teacher told me

984
01:00:11,777 --> 01:00:15,406
Keep running through my head

985
