Living a lie

994
01:00:58,857 --> 01:01:02,623
Shirlee Kenyon? Hey, Steve,
do we know a Shirlee Kenyon?

995
01:01:02,695 --> 01:01:06,187
Yeah. Who wants to know?

996
01:01:06,265 --> 01:01:08,460
This guy down here.

997
01:01:08,534 --> 01:01:10,502
How well do you know her?

998
01:01:10,569 --> 01:01:14,130
I know her well.
I know her very, very well.

999
01:01:14,206 --> 01:01:17,607
Huh. How did you meet her?

1000
01:01:19,211 --> 01:01:21,577
How did I meet who?

1001
01:01:23,716 --> 01:01:25,684
Shirlee Kenyon.

1002
01:01:28,253 --> 01:01:31,313
Well, my best friend
married her three times.

1003
01:01:31,390 --> 01:01:36,054
When he got done marrying her,
she moved in with me...

1004
01:01:36,128 --> 01:01:40,155
and I didn't even
have to marry her once.

1005
01:01:40,232 --> 01:01:43,497
- She married the same guy three times.
- Yeah.

1006
01:01:43,569 --> 01:01:45,816
Why are you asking
all these questions?

1007
01:01:45,817 --> 01:01:48,063
Credit check.

1008
01:01:48,140 --> 01:01:51,303
What'd you say your name was?

1009
01:01:52,411 --> 01:01:54,641
- Mack.
- Listen, Mack.

1010
01:01:59,351 --> 01:02:01,911
Do you give credit...

1011
01:02:01,987 --> 01:02:05,388
to people who steal
other people's bowling bags?

1012
01:02:11,296 --> 01:02:14,493
And I sacrificed my honor

1013
